{"tid":1321654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［必看］其實宜家最需要係前線警理解呢件事2","createTime":"2019-07-15T17:24:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T18:10:20.000Z","uid":153017,"like":12,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"544f7ad11aeb9b01d7b63ecff7924effc246a39a","tid":1321654,"uid":153017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:24:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">換台重po</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果你係警，或者你朋友係警</span> <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">求下你睇一睇</span></span><br />\n<br />\n條片提及左幾個point好值得參考 <br />\n<br />\n-香港搞到咁 所有起因黎自淋病 <br />\n<br />\n-如果淋病被逼落左台下一個就係盧狗窿 所以警方高層係同淋病同一條船<br />\n<br />\n-（淋病：我唔會出賣警隊）既意思唔係指唔會出賣警察 其實佢只係指唔會出賣 警方高層 佢唔撚會理你d前線警死幾多人<br />\n<br />\n-依家淋病成功將市民既目標分散左俾警 令自己有盾牌同有人陪葬<br />\n<br />\n-警員受傷 市民受傷 淋病毫無損傷<br />\n<br />\n-警方高層故意命令前線警沖入商場捉人（為咗不斷製造暴動，比淋病有機會向中共假報告話黑衣人係暴徒，然後用前線警嘅武力話佢平暴，從中得到中共證明）<br />\n<br />\n-淋病唔撚會理你打我地有幾大力 你搏表現都冇用 純粹只係送你去死 黎向中共 證明佢係做到野 其實你真係只係炮灰<br />\n<br />\n-所以其實不論乜嘢遊行最後都高層都係會命令前線警員沖打我地<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">結論：前線警員只係炮灰 輸緊嘅係市民同前線警 贏緊嘅係政府同警方高層<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">暫時最好嘅方法 就係前線警可以理解而家嘅局勢 每次被命令衝擊我哋 只係輕輕力推撞 就已經乜都夠</span><br />\n又或者最好就係全部前線警都識反<br />\n<br />\n當所有前線警理解呢個局 就會知佢哋其實冇得益 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大膽講句其實香港人真係可以同低層警企同一條線</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">*如果全部前線警都識諗*</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">樣贏嘅就係香港 唔係中國</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我就唔信高層會炒晒全香港既警員 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n希望我冇理解錯條片既point 大家可以禁入去睇<br />\n（唔知有冇人share過，如果已經有就當我重推）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8JLHjmJIDGc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8JLHjmJIDGc&d=VPbJsUOTS2%2BU35Cb01K8cC%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=3898dd8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8JLHjmJIDGc</a>"},{"pid":"fe12e1494e8f321cd667345e804cd02dd382be7a","tid":1321654,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:24:58.000Z","msg":"【我冇嘢講2.0】<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>有人冒警！</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1319116\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1319116</a><br />\n<br />\n推post時幫手廣傳有人冒警！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>被動變主動</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">有人冒警！\n你扮警察\n涉嫌冒警及傷人\n涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器\n我地行使公民逮捕權</code></pre>"},{"pid":"f3686e38a9a516de0900590c5ba67f34eec86f9e","tid":1321654,"uid":153017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:25:05.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"0b4cd820077ce55b80d05a889a59f4003753bff0","tid":1321654,"uid":153017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:25:37.000Z","msg":"推到前線警睇倒"},{"pid":"9f5e0c4dfef0726e2967e0ee7c63f185ce09f92d","tid":1321654,"uid":153017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:33:36.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"512291d4bbf6e05a1da85158fc229a125ae6497f","tid":1321654,"uid":230890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:37:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b9f14070f13f5a59d6a278441fa1509e8a604639","tid":1321654,"uid":217418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:49:31.000Z","msg":"重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa8b331ef7c7f00d916b9a722232db77addae0a1","tid":1321654,"uid":153017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:50:17.000Z","msg":"幫手推推原po<br />\n<br />\n［必看］其實依家最需要係前線警去理解呢件事<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1321575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1321575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7a51e89db1774a378d4e8cbd4