<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大膽講句其實香港人真係可以同低層警企同一條線</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">*如果全部前線警都識諗*</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">樣贏嘅就係香港 唔係中國</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我就唔信高層會炒晒全香港既警員 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n希望我冇理解錯條片既point 大家可以禁入去睇<br />\n（唔知有冇人share過，如果已經有就當我重推）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8JLHjmJIDGc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8JLHjmJIDGc&d=VPbJsUOTS2%2BU35Cb01K8cC%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=3898dd8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8JLHjmJIDGc</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:55:40.000Z","msg":"好難聽喎條片<br />\n<br />\n有一個係phone in delay 晒"},{"pid":"09af518db1a86c7e8edf195db4680eebcf7fe8fe","tid":1321654,"uid":60120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:01:03.000Z","msg":"其實有幾難諗<br />\n每次示威都要交差，如果唔係白衫點升職<br />\n尋日沙田咪又係因為和平清場冇人拉先要圍堵商場拉返幾十個走<br />\n做得咁辛苦打黎打去，不如拉曬啲有不在場證據既交差算啦<br />\n共產黨笑得咁開心，做場戲俾佢睇囉"},{"pid":"3226356fd68d37a72652b92ac5c46f2b15e7a985","tid":1321654,"uid":37055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:10:20.000Z","msg":"大家都係香港人 同熱愛這片土地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}